<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.5.9">
<l>toṇṭā miṉamu mimaiyōrun tuṇainūṉ mārpi ṉantaṇarum</l>
<l>aṇṭā vemakkē yaruḷāyeṉ ṟaṇayuṅ kōyi larukellām</l>
<l>vaṇṭārp poḻiliṉ paḻaṉattu vayali ṉayalē kayalpāya</l>
<l>taṇṭā maraikaḷ mukamalarttuñ cāḷak kirāma maṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Heart, take refuge in Śālagrāma where fresh lotuses turn their faces,</l>
<l>As kayal fish jump next to the tended rice fields of the bee-filled groves,</l>
<l>All near the temple where gather clusters of devotees, unblinking [celestials],</l>
<l>And Brahmins, chests with strung threads, saying, “Lord, grant us grace.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
